reviewText: Was a little disappointing as it did not show enough Jay Z clips of historical events as it showed for Beyonce SSS (Super Sweet & Sexy.) However, some of the information was interestingly illuminating but not enough to satisfy me based on how much I paid for the dvd.

When I purchased this product I thought that there would be two stories of Jay and Bey then they would go into both and intertwine their careers and relationship. There were two DVDs. One for Jay-Z and one for Beyonce'. SEPARATE!!! I got a terrible DVD of Beyonce's career(seemed almost bootlegged an a little inaccurate) that mentioned Jay once or twice from a professional standpoint not from their relationship and I was too upset to watch the Jay-Z video. This is not worth one cent and the videos are old from 2003 and not current!!
